cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.CR, cs.NE 

The paper deals with pattern recognition and classifier incongruence, which are topics that fall under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel divergence measure, which is related to probability and decision-making, making it relevant to the sub-category of neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
